@ishamahabal is an entrepreneur and hairstylist. As a curly haired girl, she’s always had to take a little extra care of her hair, this inspired her to start her own Salon -  @thealchemicbeauty , specially for the curly haired girlies. She also started her own brand- @thecurlcoindia , which works wonders, how do we know? We can’t stop staring at her hair ✨
